SADNESS
Sadness is the broken heart of a child when their parents get a divorce.
Sadness is when a family member dies and you never got the chance to meet them.
Sadness is a hardened heart when there are no friends for you to turn to.
Sadness is when your best friend decides that they hate you.
Sadness is when a pregnant woman finds out that they had a miscarriage.
Sadness is all around as you see the problems in this perfect world.

